/// emphasis on proverbs/karin magana and culture, where confidence in
/// accuracy is highest), written literature (kept to general/author-level
/// facts rather than detailed plot analysis), and culture. Original
/// questions written for UI Post-UTME practice, calibrated against the
/// JAMB Hausa bank's style and accuracy-risk approach but not copied from
/// it.
